{"tid":1077820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡城稱離世沙拿合約不具法律效力 拒絕支付轉會費","createTime":"2019-03-26T00:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T01:15:54.000Z","uid":6103,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c6282657d6506bef60d6c19e733449d6ab4cc7","tid":1077820,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:19:28.000Z","msg":"卡城稱離世沙拿合約不具法律效力 拒絕支付轉會費<br />\n<br />\n英國BBC報道，英超卡迪夫城將會向國際足協表示，冬窗在法甲南特收購的前鋒伊美利安奴沙拿，由於未註冊成為英超球員，便已於本年1月21日不幸離世，卡城認為沙拿的合約不具法律效力，因而拒絕支付1,500萬鎊的轉會費。<br />\n<br />\n惟南特方面聲稱，相關轉會手續已經完成，目前已將事件轉交國際足協處理，並要求卡迪夫城在下月3日前提交證據。英超BBC報道，沙拿生前是在1月19日宣佈會轉投卡城，根據轉會協議必須在1月22日前成功註冊，惜沙拿就在1月21日不幸遇上空難。卡城發言人稱現階段正處理下月3日前，向國際足協提交證據回應事件，目前正在處理當中，現階段不作進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59411770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59411770&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=42207fee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59411770&h=7bb31d55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59411770</a>"},{"pid":"f019039dfbe988c581cd2347e7a935f9f7f396c8","tid":1077820,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4dbf8f305889d91d56a0be5812f58de1b2e41ff","tid":1077820,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b8c6282657d6506bef60d6c19e733449d6ab4cc7","tid":1077820,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:19:28.000Z","msg":"卡城稱離世沙拿合約不具法律效力 拒絕支付轉會費<br />\n<br />\n英國BBC報道，英超卡迪夫城將會向國際足協表示，冬窗在法甲南特收購的前鋒伊美利安奴沙拿，由於未註冊成為英超球員，便已於本年1月21日不幸離世，卡城認為沙拿的合約不具法律效力，因而拒絕支付1,500萬鎊的轉會費。<br />\n<br />\n惟南特方面聲稱，相關轉會手續已經完成，目前已將事件轉交國際足協處理，並要求卡迪夫城在下月3日前提交證據。英超BBC報道，沙拿生前是在1月19日宣佈會轉投卡城，根據轉會協議必須在1月22日前成功註冊，惜沙拿就在1月21日不幸遇上空難。卡城發言人稱現階段正處理下月3日前，向國際足協提交證據回應事件，目前正在處理當中，現階段不作進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59411770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59411770&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=42207fee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59411770&h=7bb31d55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59411770</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"其實搵個agent 賠就岩"},{"pid":"34c654b5200c640df2b2738d7f84a9b95aa859e3","tid":1077820,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:20:40.000Z","msg":"合理喎"},{"pid":"f1130c6f28549b887ac40e8ebb45fe3d1a9200e7","tid":1077820,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:24:09.000Z","msg":"貨物未到前損毀<br />\n可以退錢"},{"pid":"51eaeed8d992c7499f54d0b75a4f6579e8d36b18","tid":1077820,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:24:54.000Z","msg":"有保險？"},{"pid":"e55d63d3154cc54adb3deb9684dc5dcd79557e08","tid":1077820,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:26:24.000Z","msg":"都未交樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b267184e772e55e2ed76af570bd5c9c7d84358","tid":1077820,"uid":41420,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"坦白講呢單係公說公有理，婆說婆有理，俾一半好來好去算啦"},{"pid":"c674aacc24e74a42df09ef9363977820e71735fa","tid":1077820,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:27:31.000Z","msg":"根據合約冇錯<br />\n但人情睇下可唔可以俾d"},{"pid":"99cccdc30925b98c52a122f8cb874a0f0b116096","tid":1077820,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c674aacc24e74a42